00:00:00.740 --> 00:00:07.740
Hi I'm Tatiana from Sony and I'm
gonna show you how to set up your tablet

00:00:11.110 --> 00:00:14.750
and wireless speaker system to stream
music with a simple tap

00:00:14.750 --> 00:00:19.619
your personal music can be streamed
wirelessly to the speaker from your

00:00:19.619 --> 00:00:21.490
computer,smartphone or tablet

00:00:21.490 --> 00:00:25.619
not only that you can use the wireless
speaker with your smartphone to take

00:00:25.619 --> 00:00:26.099
calls

00:00:26.099 --> 00:00:30.429
with the built-in speakerphone for my
demonstration I'm using an Xperia Tablet Z

00:00:30.429 --> 00:00:31.130
 

00:00:31.130 --> 00:00:35.719
Kitchen edition and a Sony Premium
Bluetooth Speaker.  Lets get started!

00:00:35.719 --> 00:00:40.510
first you will need to access the tablet
setting to enable the One-touch feature

00:00:40.510 --> 00:00:43.620
to allow data exchange between two
devices

00:00:43.620 --> 00:00:46.969
tap on apps from the upper right corner
of the screen

00:00:46.969 --> 00:00:51.730
then tap Settings icon well in the
settings menu select more and select

00:00:51.730 --> 00:00:52.829
One-touch NFC

00:00:52.829 --> 00:00:57.809
which stands for Near Field
Communication. click on the box to put a

00:00:57.809 --> 00:00:58.449
checkmark

00:00:58.449 --> 00:01:03.000
while in this menu make sure that the
Bluetooth setting is set to On

00:01:03.000 --> 00:01:06.500
exit the settings menu by clicking on the
Home menu

00:01:06.500 --> 00:01:11.010
next you will need to pair the premium
Bluetooth speaker system to the

00:01:11.010 --> 00:01:14.070
tablet make sure Bluetooth switch is
set to On

00:01:14.070 --> 00:01:18.360
on the back of the speaker then on the
side of a speaker press and hold the

00:01:18.360 --> 00:01:19.200
pairing button

00:01:19.200 --> 00:01:22.500
until a blue light flashes rapidly and
beeps

00:01:22.549 --> 00:01:27.009
using One-touch NFC
technology you can

00:01:27.009 --> 00:01:32.390
easily connect and reconnect Bluetooth
devices touch the back with a tablet

00:01:32.390 --> 00:01:34.700
using the wireless speaker where there's
an "N"

00:01:34.700 --> 00:01:39.909
displayed on both devices the speaker
will make a sound and the screen on a

00:01:39.909 --> 00:01:43.259
tablet will ask if you want to pair the
tablet with the speaker

00:01:43.259 --> 00:01:49.149
click Yes to authorize pairing start to
play your media and turn up the volume

00:01:49.149 --> 00:01:51.700
use the plus or minus on the speaker
system

00:01:51.700 --> 00:01:55.880
you are now ready to stream your music
using the premium Bluetooth speaker

00:01:55.880 --> 00:02:00.630
for more tips and tricks and how to
videos

